        "content": "The people of The Rift adore the crown. Approval of {{player name}}'s rule is absolute. Citizens speak the ruler's name with pride and genuine loyalty. Guards stand tall and are honored to serve. Merchants thrive under the crown's favor. Riften celebrates its ruler.",
