        "content": "The Church of Skyrim has been officially established in The Rift. The old Divines' altars and shrines have been replaced with monuments to the crown. An appointed priest serves the ruler's spiritual authority in Riften. This is a permanent change that has reshaped religious life in the hold - some embrace it, others quietly resent the loss of the old ways.",
