        "content": "Faith in the crown's religious authority is absolute in Falkreath Hold. The people regard {{player name}} as divinely chosen. Priests speak of the ruler with reverence, and the faithful consider it an honor to serve the throne. Religious devotion to the crown runs deep in Falkreath.",
