        "content": "Tax rates in Falkreath Hold are punishingly high. Citizens grumble openly about the crown's greed. Merchants in Falkreath struggle to turn a profit after the taxman's cut. Common folk feel squeezed and resentful. There is growing talk that the crown takes too much and gives too little in return.",
