        "content": "Tax rates in Falkreath Hold are crushing and oppressive. The people are being bled dry. Citizens of Falkreath speak of the crown as a tyrant who cares nothing for the common folk. Merchants are closing shop. Families cannot afford basic necessities. There is open anger and desperation in the streets.",
