      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "get_global_value(\"AAIsHighKing\") == 1 and get_global_value(\"AAApprovalSkyrim\") <= 30",
        "content": "Approval of {{player name}}'s rule across Skyrim as a whole is dangerously low. The ruler is widely disliked throughout the realm. Multiple holds are unhappy, and the kingdom teeters on the edge of widespread unrest. The crown's legitimacy is questioned openly.",
