        "condition_expr": "get_global_value(\"AAIsHighKing\") == 1 and get_global_value(\"AAKing_EconomyTier\") == 0",
        "content": "Skyrim's overall economy has collapsed. The realm is in severe recession. Trade has ground to a halt, markets are empty, and coin is desperately scarce across all holds. The crown's economic policies have failed catastrophically.",
