        "content": "The crown has been forced to sell royal artwork and treasures from Highreach Castle to fund the treasury. This is a sign of financial desperation that has not gone unnoticed. Citizens whisper about the state of the kingdom's finances when even the throne room's decorations are being auctioned off.",
