        "content": "A child from The Reach has been sold by order of the crown. A shadow hangs over Markarth. Parents are afraid and angry. The stone city that has endured Forsworn raids and Dwemer ruins now faces a different kind of horror - the knowledge that the crown itself is a threat to its children.",
