        "content": "A child from Hjaalmarch has been sold by order of the crown. Morthal is grief-stricken. The small, quiet town has been shaken to its core. Nights are quieter than usual - people are grieving. The swamp town that survived vampires and civil war now mourns a child lost not to monsters, but to the crown's desperation.",
