        "content": "The crown has sold its own adopted child to fund the treasury. This is the most extreme and reviled act of desperation imaginable. The rumors have spread like wildfire across all of Skyrim. People speak of it in hushed, horrified tones. No amount of gold can wash away this stain. The ruler who would sell their own blood is regarded with a mixture of pity and disgust by all who hear of it.",
