        "content": "Disturbing rumors have reached every corner of Skyrim - the crown has sold children to fund the failing treasury. Details are murky and vary from hold to hold, but the core of the story remains: desperate times have driven the ruler to an unforgivable act. Parents across Skyrim hold their children a little tighter.",
