      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "get_global_value(\"AAIsHighKing\") == 1 and get_global_value(\"AAKingRoyalRestDay\") == 1",
        "content": "The crown has decreed that Sundas is an official day of rest across Skyrim. Workers appreciate the reprieve, though the treasury takes a small hit from reduced commerce. It is a popular decree among common folk who welcome a day free from labor.",
