      {
        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "get_global_value(\"AAIsHighKing\") == 1 and get_global_value(\"AAKingDecreeStandardWeights\") == 1",
        "content": "The crown has decreed standardized weights and measures across all holds. Trade is fairer and merchants appreciate the consistency, though infrastructure costs have risen slightly to enforce it. It is seen as a mark of a thoughtful and organized ruler.",
