        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "get_global_value(\"AAIsHighKing\") == 1 and get_global_value(\"AAKingDecreeCensus\") == 1",
        "content": "The crown has ordered an official census across Skyrim. Counters are traveling the holds to tally the population. Most see it as harmless bureaucracy, though some are suspicious of why the crown wants to know exactly how many souls live under its rule.",
