        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "get_global_value(\"AAIsHighKing\") == 1 and get_global_value(\"AAKingDecreeHRFreeMarket\") == 1",
        "content": "The crown has declared Highreach an open free market. Trade flows freely with no restrictions, making it a haven for merchants. This has boosted Highreach's prosperity enormously but drawn ire from Solitude, whose traders feel undercut by the policy.",
