        "content": "The crown has enacted a Fair Wages decree ensuring better pay for laborers across Skyrim. Workers in mining towns and industrial holds are grateful, but guard and infrastructure expenses have risen to cover the mandate. The Reach and Eastmarch workers are particularly supportive.",
