        "condition_expr": "get_global_value(\"AAIsHighKing\") == 1 and get_global_value(\"AAKingResearchGrantsActive\") == 1",
        "content": "The crown has granted significant funds to the Bard's College in Solitude and the College of Winterhold. Scholars and students are grateful for the patronage, and the crown's reputation among the educated has improved. The grants are seen as an investment in Skyrim's cultural and magical heritage.",
