        "always_inject": false,
        "condition_expr": "get_global_value(\"AAIsHighKing\") == 1 and get_global_value(\"AAKingGuildTributeActive\") == 1",
        "content": "The crown has imposed mandatory weekly tributes on Skyrim's major guilds - the Thieves Guild, the Companions, and the Dark Brotherhood. Gold flows to the treasury, but the guilds and their allies are furious. Riften, Whiterun, and the holds harboring these organizations feel the sting of this decree.",
