        "content": "The crown has offered tax incentives to encourage foreign merchants to trade in Skyrim. Khajiit caravans and traveling traders from other provinces benefit greatly from this policy. Native Nord merchants are less enthusiastic, viewing it as favoritism toward outsiders.",
