        "content": "The crown has declared Riften the spiritual capital of Skyrim. Pilgrims flock there from across the realm, and the attention and gold follow. Other holds feel slighted and overlooked - their own shrines and temples diminished in importance. There is resentment that Riften was chosen above all others.",
